description:
&lt;p&gt;We would love you to come and join our team at NCUH maternity services. We are proud to say that our service was rated Good at our last CQC inspection and our goal is to ensure all our women and families receive high quality care from our exceptional teams, whilst placing high value on our staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have 2 small friendly Consultant led units and a stand- alone birth centre and work closely with our community midwifery teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are committed to supporting our staff with their professional development and have a bespoke midwifery skills training programme. All our midwives complete the NLS and are supported to undertake the NIPE course.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post will initially be based within Allerdale Community Midwives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Share and Part time hours will be considered, up to 30 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or to arrange a to visit and meet with some of our team please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Susan Kneen 01900 705033 or Rebecca Dawson 07824126537&lt;/p&gt;
